title: Switzerland Tourist Arrivals
description: Tourist Arrivals in Switzerland decreased to 1925.44 Thousand in September from 2160.60 Thousand in August of 2022. Tourist Arrivals in Switzerland averaged 1270.75 Thousand from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 2284.42 Thousand in July of 2019 and a record low of 53.92 Thousand in April of 2020. This page provides - Switzerland Tourist Arrivals - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Swiss Federal Statistical Office
